{"tid":1452690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經打咗去食環跟進葵芳站嘅食物會否受到污染","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:10:56.000Z","uid":268272,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"703b0df0e6307442479595eb52454e1959bbb107","tid":1452690,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅大家連登巴打都知道葵芳站內放咗tear gas<br />\n裏面都有好多食肆例如東海堂、唐記包點、華御結等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我費事大家買嘢食嗰陣時有tear gas放題<br />\n食到五光十色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就幫手打咗去食環署嘅1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係義士面前打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋已經攞咗檔案編號了<br />\n如果佢仲未回覆我嘅話<br />\n就繼續打電話去跟進下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果嗰幾個義士有連登的話<br />\n麻煩幫手作證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSor for 冇錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zCvua5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zCvua5.png&h=f7388774&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d154b62d270298d9fc4117fca9cb20e5261fd308","tid":1452690,"uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"消防， 環保處， 屋宇署"},{"pid":"7b12f142c917ea596299e7f5f408d5e483dacd75","tid":1452690,"uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"仲有emsd"},{"pid":"6a882716be387539835d73c6c96eb6002e96486d","tid":1452690,"uid":64356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8376940a4e0405301bda1ddca7e0c4f8e8b4edb9","tid":1452690,"uid":263251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"703b0df0e6307442479595eb52454e1959bbb107","tid":1452690,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"